            <title>日內瓦國際發明展得獎名單出爐，香港獲逾 350 獎 + 中國 70 項發明獲金獎</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/22/geneva-international-exhibition-of-inventions-2024/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=geneva-international-exhibition-of-inventions-2024</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/22/geneva-international-exhibition-of-inventions-2024/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 08:30:26 +0000</pubDate>
